<headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 07 at 12:41AM EDT  by NWS Buffalo</headline>
<description>...Heavy Rain Likely Through 2 AM...
An area of showers and thunderstorms will cross Niagara county
through 2 AM. Tropical downpours within this activity could drop
an inch and a half of rain on some areas in less than an hours
time, so significant ponding on area roadways along with some poor
drainage flooding will be possible.</description>
